Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:57.23,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}今キミがどこにいたって
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.24,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}変わるはずないよね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:07.41,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}心はいつでも 繋がってる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.33,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}遠く離れていても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:14.13,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}忘れずにいてね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:17.92,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}あの日感じた情熱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:21.92,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}ふたりで重ねた夢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:28.35,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}茜色の空 沈んでく夕陽
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.77,0:22:37.27,edj,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}私らしく 歩いていこう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.20,0:21:32.04,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}在被夕陽染紅的坡道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.38,0:21:39.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}停下腳步駐足停留的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:46.01,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}總是不經意想起遠去的你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:53.02,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我試著找回快要迷失的道路
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.35,0:21:57.23,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}無論你現在身處何方
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.28,0:22:00.24,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}也不會有任何變化吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.45,0:22:07.41,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}我們的心始終緊緊連繫著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.49,0:22:11.33,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}儘管彼此相隔遙遠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.46,0:22:14.13,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}也請別忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.17,0:22:17.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}那一天感受到的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.21,0:22:21.92,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}兩人曾經一起追逐的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.97,0:22:28.35,edc,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be1\blur1.5}暗紅色的天空 逐漸下沉的夕陽
